
README for Physics
==================

Name:                   Physics
License:                LGPL
Maintainer:             Behboud Kalantary <behboud.kalantary@igd.fhg.de>
Initial Author:         Behboud Kalantary <behboud.kalantary@igd.fhg.de>
Additional Libraries:   ODE (http://opende.sourceforge.net
Added:                  2005/07/08
Last modified:          2005/07/08
Last tested:            2005/07/08

Description:

This lib wraps the ODE functions for OpenSG. Tested only with the static ODE lib!
Not all methods are implemented into FieldContainer classes. Thus, when you save a
osb file, things like mass are not stored. This is something todo. Feel free to complete
the supported functions.

Coded at the Fraunhofer Institut für Graphische Datenverarbeitung - Abteilung für
Industrielle Anwendungen ( IGD - A2)

Configure:
./configure <your profile > --with-add-lib=ode:ode

Many thanks to Anreas Zieringer and Christian Lessig

Have fun

    BK
